VALUES ('6fe26fcb-35b3-4700-ae92-28569e7216ed', 'Which choice completes the text with the most logical transition?', 'Critics initially dismissed the novelist''s dense, footnote-laden style as a barrier that would keep ordinary readers away. The books became runaway bestsellers anyway, embraced precisely by the general audience the critics had written off. ______ the very feature the reviewers treated as a liability turned out to be the source of the novels'' popular appeal.', NULL, '[{"id":"A","text":"Indeed,","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: the final sentence intensifies and confirms the surprising point that the off-putting style actually drew readers in."},{"id":"B","text":"However,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Wrong: the final sentence reinforces rather than reverses the preceding sentence about popular embrace."},{"id":"C","text":"By comparison,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Wrong: no second item is being measured against the first; the sentence restates the same surprise more emphatically."},{"id":"D","text":"In conclusion,","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Wrong: this two-step passage is not a summary of multiple points but an emphatic confirmation of one."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Identify the relationship
The middle sentence says the books were {{yellow:embraced precisely by the general audience the critics had written off}}, and the final sentence drives that irony home.
Step 2 — Match the transition
Since the last sentence strengthens and confirms the point just made, the emphatic ''Indeed'' fits.
Distractor analysis:
- B: ''However'' marks contrast, but the closing sentence agrees with the prior one.
- C: ''By comparison'' needs two things to compare; only one phenomenon is discussed.
- D: ''In conclusion'' suits a wrap-up of several points, not a single intensifying restatement.', 'Decide whether the final line contradicts, summarizes, or emphatically confirms the surprise.', 'Expression of Ideas', 'Transitions', 'reading_writing', 'expression', 'TRA', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"generator":"scholaris_ai_v1","model":"gemma-4-26b-a4b-it","original":true,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
